Package: straightliner
Title: Check Survey Responses Using a Variety of Straightlining Measures
Version: 0.9.0.0
Date: 
Authors@R: 
    person("Max", "weylandt", , "mweylandt@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre"),
           comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0001-8590-4145"))
Description: This package implements several quantiative measures of straigtlining
    as descriped in Kim et al. (2019). It offers a user-friendly way to assess 
    whether individual are straightlining, or compare sets of questions against 
    one another to see if people straightline more in some batteries than in others.
